flowchart LR
    SRC[Public Datasets] --> ING[Glue Bronze Ingestion Job]
    ING --> BRZ[S3 Bronze]

    BRZ --> TRN[Glue Silver Transform Job]
    TRN --> SLV[S3 Silver]
    TRN --> QTN[S3 Quarantine]
    ING --> AUD[S3 Audit and Checkpoints]
    TRN --> AUD

    SLV --> GLD_JOB[Glue Gold Build Job]
    GLD_JOB --> GLD[S3 Gold]

    GLD --> ATH[Athena Workgroup]
    GLD --> BI[QuickSight and Superset Datasets]

    SFN[Step Functions State Machine] --> ING
    SFN --> TRN
    SFN --> GLD_JOB

    MET[Pipeline Metrics] --> CW[CloudWatch Alarms]
    ING --> MET
    TRN --> MET
    GLD_JOB --> MET
